#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.40:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga "
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 40. Vādatthikasutta → vādasuttaṃ (bj) | vādino (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Vādatthikasutta "
msgstr "40. Looking For a Debate "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.40:1.1"
msgid "“Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … "
msgstr "“Mendicants, take any mendicant who truly understands: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:1.2"
msgid "‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, puratthimāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā vādatthiko vādagavesī: "
msgstr "An ascetic or brahmin might come from the east, west, north, or south wanting to debate, seeking a debate, thinking: "

# NOTE: BB seems to omit sahadhammena
msgctxt "sn56.40:1.3"
msgid "‘vādamassa āropessāmī’ti, taṃ vata sahadhammena saṅkampessati vā sampakampessati vā sampacālessati vāti—netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "‘I’ll refute their doctrine!’ It’s simply impossible for them to legitimately make that mendicant shake or rock or tremble. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:1.4"
msgid "Pacchimāya cepi disāya … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.40:1.5"
msgid "uttarāya cepi disāya … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.40:1.6"
msgid "dakkhiṇāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā vādatthiko vādagavesī: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.40:1.7"
msgid "‘vādamassa āropessāmī’ti, taṃ vata sahadhammena saṅkampessati vā sampakampessati vā sampacālessati vāti—netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.446, sc2
msgctxt "sn56.40:2.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, silāyūpo soḷasa kukkuko. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a stone pillar, sixteen feet long. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.2"
msgid "Tassassu aṭṭha kukku heṭṭhā nemaṅgamā, aṭṭha kukku uparinemassa. "
msgstr "Eight feet were buried underground, and eight above ground. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.3"
msgid "Puratthimāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya bhusā vātavuṭṭhi, neva saṅkampeyya na sampakampeyya na sampacāleyya; pacchimāya cepi disāya … pe … uttarāya cepi disāya … pe … dakkhiṇāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya bhusā vātavuṭṭhi, neva saṅkampeyya na sampakampeyya na sampacāleyya. "
msgstr "Even if violent storms were to blow up out of the east, the west, the north, and the south, they couldn’t make it shake or rock or tremble. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.5"
msgid "Gambhīrattā, bhikkhave, nemassa sunikhātattā silāyūpassa. "
msgstr "It’s because that boundary pillar is firmly embedded, with deep foundations. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.40:2.6"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhikkhave, yo hi koci bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "In the same way, take any mendicant who truly understands: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.7"
msgid "puratthimāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā vādatthiko vādagavesī ‘vādamassa āropessāmī’ti, taṃ vata sahadhammena saṅkampessati vā sampakampessati vā sampacālessati vāti—netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "An ascetic or brahmin might come from the east, west, north, or south wanting to debate, seeking a debate, thinking: ‘I’ll refute their doctrine!’ It’s simply impossible for them to legitimately make that mendicant shake or rock or tremble. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.8"
msgid "Pacchimāya cepi disāya … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.9"
msgid "uttarāya cepi disāya … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.10"
msgid "dakkhiṇāya cepi disāya āgaccheyya samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā vādatthiko vādagavesī: ‘vādamassa āropessāmī’ti, taṃ vata sahadhammena saṅkampessati vā sampakampessati vā sampacālessati vāti—netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.11"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.12"
msgid "Sudiṭṭhattā, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s because they have clearly seen the four noble truths. "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.13"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.40:2.14"
msgid "Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasaccassa. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.40:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.40:3.2"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.40:3.3"
msgid "Sīsapāvanavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn56.40:4.1"
msgid "Sīsapā khadiro daṇḍo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.40:4.2"
msgid "celā sattisatena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.40:4.3"
msgid "Pāṇā sūriyūpamā dvedhā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.40:4.4"
msgid "indakhīlo ca vādinoti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
